member.name: TfIntegratableCandidateListSelectionStyle
member.summary: Elements of the TfIntegratableCandidateListSelectionStyle enumeration specify the integratable candidate list selection styles.

member.name: TfIntegratableCandidateListSelectionStyle.STYLE_ACTIVE_SELECTION
member.summary: The selection can be changed with the arrow keys.

member.name: TfIntegratableCandidateListSelectionStyle.STYLE_IMPLIED_SELECTION
member.summary: The default selection key will choose the selection.
